snippet.title: A Gummy's Life - Launch Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Hilarious and sugary fights based on physics on the local and online party multiplayer, A Gummy's Life, where death by chocolate is a very real possibility! Tons of levels with various game styles and mechanics, many characters to choose from and tasty taunts to rub your victory in your opponents' faces!

#AGummysLife
